      <title>美国抵御红海袭击，以色列扩大加沙攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/israel-expands-gaza-offensive-as-us-fends-off-red-sea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方正在扩大其在加沙地带的行动，预计对加沙南部的地面入侵迫在眉睫，并警告该领土 220 万居民中的许多人再次撤离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/israel-expands-gaza-offensive-as-us-fends-off-red-sea-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 02:47:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
