    <item>
      <title>苏纳克考虑限制支出以允许英国进一步减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/sunak-considers-spending-restraint-to-allow-for-more-uk-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克首次将削减开支与减税联系起来，明确表示英国政府希望通过控制国家服务和福利支出来支付进一步减税的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/sunak-considers-spending-restraint-to-allow-for-more-uk-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在红海航运遇袭后警告伊朗支持的胡塞武装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/uk-owned-ship-hit-by-rocket-fire-in-red-sea-arabiya-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的胡塞叛军声称他们的目标是红海的“两艘以色列船只”，这是周日在国际水域针对商船的一系列袭击的一部分，美国称其中一艘驱逐舰击落了三架无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/uk-owned-ship-hit-by-rocket-fire-in-red-sea-arabiya-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 15:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚马拉皮火山爆发，登山者受伤，村庄被火山灰覆盖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-indonesia-s-marapi-volcano-erupts-spewing-ash-plumes-and-blanketing-several-villages-with-ash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚巴东 (美联社) –印度尼西亚的马拉皮山周日喷发了白色和灰色的火山灰羽流，造成登山者搁浅和受伤，火山灰散布到几个村庄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-indonesia-s-marapi-volcano-erupts-spewing-ash-plumes-and-blanketing-several-villages-with-ash</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
