      <title>莫迪的政党赢得关键州民意调查，提高第三任期的竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/modi-set-to-win-key-state-polls-boosting-bid-to-stay-in-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度执政党印度人民党赢得了三场重要的州选举，并在其中两场选举中击败了反对派，加强了总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三次连任的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/modi-set-to-win-key-state-polls-boosting-bid-to-stay-in-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
